\f0\b \cf0 ###Stay in Nature\
\pard\pardeftab720\ri720

\b0 \cf0 ![Nova Scotia Road Trip](thumb_IMG_0481_st_andrews.jpg \'93St Andews\'94) 
\f1 \

\f0 \
We ended our Canadian adventures with a trip to St. Andrews where we stayed in this small cabin in the woods on the water. It was private and quiet. Since I am a bit of an urban child, it was really foreign for me to be somewhere where there really isn\'92t another person around you. \
\
We drove into town and got some dinner, and when we came back, there was a beaver running around the deck of the cabin! I might have thought it was a cub at first \'85 maybe. In the morning, it was beautiful, cold, and sunny. I went for a run around the water and wished I could have crisp runs every day.\
